Another possible sub-category is cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) because the paper deals with the processing of speech signals and the extraction of acoustic-prosodic cues. 

The sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possibility because the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for disfluency detection.
